465
00:27:27.960 --> 00:27:29.800
- Hai.
- Hai.


466
00:27:29.880 --> 00:27:31.000
- Simone.
- Anna.


467
00:27:31.080 --> 00:27:32.640
- Anggap rumah sendiri.
- Baik.


468
00:27:32.720 --> 00:27:34.920
Anna, asalmu bukan dari Roma?

469
00:27:35.000 --> 00:27:37.720
- Bukan, aku baru pindah.
