635
00:36:39.080 --> 00:36:39.920
Bagus sekali!

636
00:36:40.000 --> 00:36:42.200
Cepat keluar. Persetan denganmu!

637
00:36:42.720 --> 00:36:44.120
Jangan pernah kembali!

638
00:36:59.040 --> 00:36:59.920
Siapa?

